      "para_id": "Q001440.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ningublaga , the king who crushes the evil-doers , Nigdu-pae , the scribe , the archivist of Irisaĝrig , child of Ur-kiri , the scribe , dedicated this ( object ) for the well-being of Šarati-gubisin , his king , for his well-being and for the well-being of his spouse and child ."
    }
  ],
